            <-----(Pseudocode)----->

Start
// Take account number
Input account number
// Check the validity of account number
If,
   account number is valid
Proceed to the Next step
Else If,
Print "This is invalid account number"
// Ask For deposite amount 
Input deposite amount
// Check the deposite amount is valid (deposite amount > 0)
If, 
   The amount is valid 
Update account balance
Else If,
   Print "Invalid deposite amount"
// Provide recept
Print "There is your recept", recept
End

            <-----(Algorithm)----->
